"title": "1205: God, titles and names of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1205",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>These reflect the great and varied aspects of God's being and character. They are particularly used by the psalmists to speak of God as a source of strength, security, blessing and hope.</p>\n<h2>Titles which denote God's greatness</h2>\n<h3>God Almighty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:1\">GEN 17:1</a></strong> <em>This was the special name by which God revealed himself to the patriarchs. The Hebrew is “El-Shaddai” possibly meaning “God the mountain”, emphasising God's might.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:3\">GEN 28:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:3\">GEN 48:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:3\">EXO 6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:20-Ruth1:21\">RUT 1:20–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:17\">JOB 5:17</a>JOB <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:4\">6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:23\">JOB 37:23</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:1\">PSA 91:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:14\">REV 16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:15\">REV 19:15</a></p>\n<h3>God Most High</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:18-Gen14:20\">GEN 14:18–14:20</a></strong> <em>The Hebrew “El-Elyon” denotes the supremacy and sovereignty of God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:22\">GEN 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:8\">DEU 32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:14\">2SA 22:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:13\">PSA 18:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:2\">PSA 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:7\">PSA 21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:4\">PSA 46:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:2\">PSA 47:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:35\">PSA 78:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:9\">PSA 97:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:14\">ISA 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:26\">DAN 3:26</a>MRK <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:7\">5:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:28\">LUK 8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32\">LUK 1:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">LUK 1:35</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:35\">LUK 6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:17\">ACT 16:17</a></p>\n<h3>The Eternal God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:33\">GEN 21:33</a></strong> <em>The Hebrew “El-Olam” only occurs in this verse.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:27\">DEU 33:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:26\">ROM 16:26</a></p>\n<h3>The Ancient of Days</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:9\">DAN 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13\">DAN 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:22\">DAN 7:22</a></p>\n<h3>The Mighty One</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:49\">LUK 1:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:22\">JOS 22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:1\">PSA 50:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:2\">PSA 132:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:5\">PSA 132:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:24\">ISA 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:26\">ISA 49:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:16\">ISA 60:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:62\">MRK 14:62</a></p>\n<h3>The living God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:2\">PSA 84:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:26-Dan6:27\">DAN 6:26–6:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:26\">DEU 5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:10\">JOS 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:26\">1SA 17:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:36\">1SA 17:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:16\">2KI 19:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:17\">ISA 37:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:2\">PSA 42:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:16\">MAT 16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:31\">HEB 10:31</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy One of Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:6\">ISA 12:6</a></strong> <em>“the Holy One of Israel” is a favourite divine title in the book of Isaiah.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:22\">2KI 19:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:23\">ISA 37:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:22\">PSA 71:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:41\">PSA 78:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:18\">PSA 89:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:12\">ISA 30:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:15\">ISA 30:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:14\">ISA 41:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:11\">ISA 45:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:5\">ISA 55:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:9\">ISA 60:9</a></p>\n<h3>The LORD</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:26\">GEN 4:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:2\">EXO 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:15\">EXO 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:5-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:5–34:7</a></p>\n<h2>Titles which refer to God as LORD</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:17\">DEU 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:10\">DEU 28:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:3\">1KI 2:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:10\">PSA 146:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:9\">JER 14:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:14\">DAN 9:14</a></p>\n<h3>The Lord God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:8\">REV 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:5\">REV 22:5</a></p>\n<h3>The LORD God Almighty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:8\">PSA 89:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:4\">PSA 80:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:14\">JER 5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:16\">JER 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:5\">HOS 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:13\">AMO 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>The LORD Most High</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:17\">PSA 7:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:2\">PSA 47:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:9\">PSA 97:9</a></p>\n<h3>The Sovereign LORD</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:28\">2SA 7:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:26\">DEU 9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:7\">JOS 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:8\">ISA 25:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:17\">JER 32:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:2\">AMO 7:2</a></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of light</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:29\">2SA 22:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1\">PSA 27:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:11\">PSA 84:11</a> <em>the sun</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:17\">ISA 10:17</a> <em>the Light of Israel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:8\">MIC 7:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a> <em>the Father of the heavenly lights</em></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of strength</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:9\">PSA 59:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:2\">EXO 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:1\">PSA 18:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:19\">PSA 22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">PSA 46:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:17\">PSA 59:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:1\">PSA 81:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:2\">ISA 12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of security</h2>\n<h3>A shield</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1\">GEN 15:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:29\">DEU 33:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:3\">2SA 22:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">PSA 18:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:31\">2SA 22:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30\">PSA 18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:11\">PSA 84:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:9\">PSA 115:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:7\">PRO 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:5\">PRO 30:5</a></p>\n<h3>A refuge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">PSA 46:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:9\">PSA 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps61:3\">PSA 61:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:2\">PSA 91:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:9\">PSA 91:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:114\">PSA 119:114</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:5\">PSA 142:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:19\">JER 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:16\">JOL 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:7\">NAM 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>A hiding-place</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:7\">PSA 32:7</a></p>\n<h3>A fortress</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:2\">2SA 22:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">PSA 18:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:3\">PSA 31:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:2\">PSA 62:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:6\">PSA 62:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:2\">PSA 91:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:2\">PSA 144:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:10\">ISA 17:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:19\">JER 16:19</a></p>\n<h3>A stronghold</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:3\">2SA 22:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">PSA 18:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:9\">PSA 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1\">PSA 27:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:39\">PSA 37:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:2\">PSA 43:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:2\">PSA 144:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:16\">JOL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>A defender</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:18\">DEU 10:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:5\">PSA 68:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:11\">PRO 23:11</a></p>\n<h3>A Rock</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:24\">GEN 49:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:14\">PSA 19:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of provision</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:14\">GEN 22:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:24\">LAM 3:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:8\">GEN 22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:26\">PSA 73:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:57\">PSA 119:57</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:5\">PSA 142:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:16\">JER 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:19\">JER 51:19</a></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of hope</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:8\">JER 14:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:13\">JER 17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:7\">JER 50:7</a></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of peace</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:33\">ROM 15:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:24\">JDG 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:20\">ROM 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:9\">PHP 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23\">1TH 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:16\">2TH 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20\">HEB 13:20</a></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of comfort</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:18\">JER 8:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3\">2CO 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of grace</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6\">EXO 34:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:31\">NEH 9:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:15\">PSA 86:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">JON 4:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>Titles referring to God as the source of love</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:10\">PSA 59:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:17\">PSA 59:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:2\">PSA 144:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7-1John4:16\">1JN 4:7–4:16</a></p>\n<h2>God as shepherd</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1\">PSA 23:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:15\">GEN 48:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:24\">GEN 49:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:1\">PSA 80:1</a></p>\n<h2>The true God</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:3\">2CH 15:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>",
